dc.title: Electronic Transfer Account (ETA) - Home Page
dc.description: ETA is a low-cost account at a Bank, Credit Union, or Savings and Loan to which a Federal benefit, wage, salary or retirement payment is deposited electronically. Visit this site to learn more about ETA and locate an ETA provider.
